B041C005V015	41	5	15	And they came to Jesus, and saw the man who had been possessed by the devil, who had the legion, sitting, and clothed, and in his right mind: and they were afraid.
B041C005V016	41	5	16	And those who saw it told what happened to the man who was possessed by the devil, and to the swine.
B041C005V017	41	5	17	And they began to beg him to depart from their region.
B041C005V018	41	5	18	And as he got into the boat, the man who had been possessed by the devil begged him that he might go with him.
B041C005V019	41	5	19	Yet Jesus did not let him, but said to him, Go home to your friends, and tell them what great things the Lord has done for you, and how he has had compassion on you.
B041C005V020	41	5	20	And he departed, and began to proclaim in Decapolis what great things Jesus had done for him: and all the people were amazed.
B041C005V021	41	5	21	And when Jesus crossed over again by boat to the other side, many people gathered around him: and he was near the sea.
B041C005V022	41	5	22	And, behold, there came one of the rulers of the synagogue, Jairus by name; and when he saw him, he fell at his feet,
B041C005V023	41	5	23	And begged him greatly, saying, My little daughter lies at the point of death: I beg you, come and lay your hands on her, that she may be healed and live.
B041C005V024	41	5	24	And Jesus went with him; and many people followed him, and crowded him.
B041C005V025	41	5	25	And a certain woman, who had a flow of blood for twelve years,
B041C005V026	41	5	26	And had suffered many things from many physicians, and had spent all that she had, and was not helped, but rather grew worse,
B041C005V027	41	5	27	When she heard of Jesus, came in the crowd from behind, and touched his garment.
B041C005V028	41	5	28	For she said, If I just touch his clothes, I shall be healed.
B041C005V029	41	5	29	And immediately the flow of blood was dried up; and she felt in her body that she was healed of the affliction.
B041C005V030	41	5	30	And Jesus, immediately knowing that power had gone out of him, turned around in the crowd, and said, Who touched my clothes?
B041C005V031	41	5	31	And his disciples said to him, You see the multitude crowding you, and you say, Who touched me?
B041C005V032	41	5	32	And he looked around to see the woman who had done this thing.
