B041C005V034	41	5	34	And he said to her, Daughter, your faith has made you well; go in peace, and be healed of your affliction.
B041C005V035	41	5	35	While he was speaking, messengers came from the ruler of the synagogue's house and said, Your daughter is dead: why trouble the Teacher further?
B041C005V036	41	5	36	As soon as Jesus heard what was spoken, he said to the ruler of the synagogue, Do not be afraid, only believe.
