B041C005V038	41	5	38	And he came to the house of the ruler of the synagogue, and saw the tumult, and those who wept and wailed greatly.
B041C005V039	41	5	39	And when he had come in, he said to them, Why do you make this tumult, and weep? the child is not dead, but sleeps.
