B041C006V025	41	6	25	And she came immediately in haste to the king, and asked, saying, I want you to give me right now the head of John the Baptist on a platter.
B041C006V026	41	6	26	The king was exceedingly sorry; yet for his oath's sake, and for the sake of those who sat with him, he would not refuse her.
