B041C008V008	41	8	8	So they ate, and were filled: and of the broken pieces that were left over they picked up seven baskets.
B041C008V009	41	8	9	And there were about four thousand people: and he sent them away.
B041C008V010	41	8	10	And immediately he entered into a boat with his disciples, and went to the district of Dalmanutha.
B041C008V011	41	8	11	And the Pharisees came forth, and began to question him, seeking from him a sign from heaven, testing him.
B041C008V012	41	8	12	And he sighed deeply in his spirit, and said, Why does this generation seek after a sign? truly I say to you, There shall be no sign given to this generation.
B041C008V013	41	8	13	And he left them, and entering into the boat again departed to the other side.
