B041C008V028	41	8	28	And they answered, John the Baptist: but some say, Elijah; and others, One of the prophets.
B041C008V029	41	8	29	And he said to them, But who do you say that I am? And Peter answered and said to him, You are the Christ.
B041C008V030	41	8	30	And he commanded them that they should tell no man about him.
B041C008V031	41	8	31	And he began to teach them, that the Son of man must suffer many things, and be rejected by the elders, and by the chief priests, and scribes, and be killed, and after three days rise again.
