B042C005V038	42	5	38	But new wine must be put into new skins; then both are preserved.
B042C005V039	42	5	39	And no man having drunk old wine desires the new: for he says, The old is better.
B042C006V001	42	6	1	And it came to pass on the second sabbath after the first, that he went through the grain fields; and his disciples plucked the ears of grain, and ate them, rubbing them in their hands.
