B042C006V003	42	6	3	And Jesus answered and said to them, Have you not even read what David did, when he was hungry, he and those who were with him;
B042C006V004	42	6	4	How he went into the house of God, and took and ate the showbread, and gave also to those who were with him; although it is not lawful for anyone but the priests to eat of it?
B042C006V005	42	6	5	And he said to them, The Son of man is Lord of the sabbath.
