B042C006V017	42	6	17	And he came down with them, and stood on a level place; and there was the company of his disciples and a great multitude of people out of all Judaea and Jerusalem, and from the seacoast of Tyre and Sidon, who came to hear him, and to be healed of their diseases;
B042C006V018	42	6	18	And those who were troubled with unclean spirits were healed.
B042C006V019	42	6	19	And the whole multitude sought to touch him: for power came from him, and healed them all.
B042C006V020	42	6	20	And he lifted up his eyes on his disciples, and said, Blessed are you who are poor: for yours is the kingdom of God.
